content: I'm looking for some recipes for bread, I just found my old bread maker while unpacking a box from my move and I want to start using it again. Do you have any simple recipes for beginners? By the way, I'm feeling pretty accomplished after organizing my closet a couple of Sundays ago - I ended up donating three bags of clothes to Goodwill and getting rid of a bunch of old shoes that were no longer wearable.
